<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr" class="scroll-smooth">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/jpeg" href="/image/shardtown.jpeg">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shardtown | Wiki</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #000000;
            --text: #ffffff;
            --accent: #ffffff;
            --muted: #888888;
            --border: #1a1a1a;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif;
            background: #000;
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(at 50% 0%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 0% 100%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.1) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 100% 100%, rgba(236, 72, 153, 0.1) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 50% 50%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05) 0px, transparent 50%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text);
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .bg-glow {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 100%;
            height: 100vh;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .container-wide {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 24px;
        }

        .nav-link {
            color: var(--muted);
            transition: color 0.2s;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .nav-link:hover { color: var(--text); }

        .btn-white {
            background: #fff;
            color: #000;
            padding: 10px 24px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-white:hover { opacity: 0.9; }

        .wiki-sidebar-link {
            display: block;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
            transition: all 0.2s;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .wiki-sidebar-link:hover { color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
        .wiki-sidebar-link.active { color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.07); }

        .wiki-card {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            border: 1px solid #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            scroll-margin-top: 120px;
        }

        .wiki-card:hover { border-color: #2a2a2a; }

        .feature-chip {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .chip-guard { background: rgba(37,99,235,0.1); color: #60a5fa; border: 1px solid rgba(37,99,235,0.2); }
        .chip-shard { background: rgba(139,92,246,0.1); color: #a78bfa; border: 1px solid rgba(139,92,246,0.2); }

        .step-badge {
            width: 28px;
            height: 28px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .command-block {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px 18px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #a78bfa;
        }

        .var-tag {
            background: rgba(37,99,235,0.15);
            color: #93c5fd;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 2px 8px;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 14px;
            padding: 14px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
        }

        .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; padding-bottom: 0; }
        .info-row:first-child { padding-top: 0; }

        .section-divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, rgba(255,255,255,0.06), transparent);
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="bg-glow"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="fixed top-6 left-0 right-0 z-50 px-6">
        <header id="main-header" class="container-wide flex justify-between items-center bg-transparent rounded-full transition-all duration-300 py-4 px-8 border border-white/10">
            <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
                <img src="/image/shardtown.jpeg" alt="Shardtown Logo" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full object-cover">
                <span class="font-bold tracking-tight text-xl uppercase">Shardtown</span>
            </a>
            <nav class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-8">
                <a href="/#products" class="nav-link">Produits</a>
                <a href="/#services" class="nav-link">Services</a>
                <a href="/#about" class="nav-link">À propos</a>
                <a href="/wiki" class="nav-link" style="color:#fff">Wiki</a>
                <a href="/#status" class="nav-link">Statut</a>
            </nav>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                    <div class="hidden md:flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full border border-white/5">
                        <img src="https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/<%= user.id %>/<%= user.avatar %>.png" class="w-7 h-7 rounded-full border border-white/10" alt="">
                        <span class="font-bold text-sm"><%= user.username %></span>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-white">Dashboard</a>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-white">Dashboard</a>
            <% } %>
        </header>
    </div>

    <script>
        console.log(
            '%c' +
            '███  █  █  ██  ███  ███  ████  ██  █   █ █  █\n' +
            '█    █  █ █  █ █  █ █  █  █   █  █ █   █ ██ █\n' +
            '███  ████ ████ ███  █  █  █   █  █ █ █ █ █ ██\n' +
            '  █  █  █ █  █ █ █  █  █  █   █  █ ██ ██ █  █\n' +
            '███  █  █ █  █ █  █ ███   █    ██  █   █ █  █\n',
            'color: #3b82f6; font-family: monospace; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1; font-weight: bold;'
        );
        console.log('%c© 2026 Shardtown — shardtown.fr', 'color: #444; font-family: monospace; font-size: 10px;');

        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const header = document.getElementById('main-header');
            if (window.scrollY > 50) {
                header.classList.remove('bg-transparent', 'border-white/10');
                header.classList.add('bg-white/5', 'backdrop-blur-lg', 'border-white/5');
            } else {
                header.classList.add('bg-transparent', 'border-white/10');
                header.classList.remove('bg-white/5', 'backdrop-blur-lg', 'border-white/5');
            }
        });
    </script>

    <main class="pt-40 pb-24">
        <div class="container-wide">

            <!-- Hero -->
            <div class="mb-16 text-center">
                <p class="text-sm font-bold tracking-widest text-white/40 uppercase mb-4">Documentation</p>
                <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-5">WIKI</h1>
                <p class="text-white/40 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Tout ce que vous devez savoir pour configurer et utiliser les bots Shardtown.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex gap-12 items-start">

                <!-- Sidebar -->
                <aside class="hidden lg:block w-60 shrink-0 sticky top-32">
                    <p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/20 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4 px-3">Navigation</p>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 px-3">Général</p>
                        <a href="#intro" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Introduction</a>
                        <a href="#dashboard" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Dashboard Web</a>
                    </div>

                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 px-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <img src="/image/shardguard.png" class="w-4 h-4 rounded" alt=""> ShardGuard
                        </p>
                        <a href="#sg-verification" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Vérification Captcha</a>
                        <a href="#sg-automod" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Auto-Modération</a>
                        <a href="#sg-warnings" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Avertissements</a>
                        <a href="#sg-stats" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Canaux de Stats</a>
                        <a href="#sg-logs" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Logs</a>
                        <a href="#sg-commands" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Commandes</a>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/40 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 px-3 flex items-center gap-2">
                            <img src="/image/shard.png" class="w-4 h-4 rounded" alt=""> Shard
                        </p>
                        <a href="#s-welcome" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Bienvenue / Départ</a>
                        <a href="#s-autorole" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Rôle Automatique</a>
                        <a href="#s-levels" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Niveaux & XP</a>
                        <a href="#s-tempvoice" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Salons Vocaux Temp.</a>
                        <a href="#s-reactions" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Auto-Réactions</a>
                        <a href="#s-commands" class="wiki-sidebar-link">Commandes</a>
                    </div>
                </aside>

                <!-- Content -->
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">

                    <!-- INTRO -->
                    <div id="intro" class="wiki-card">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                            <div class="step-badge"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg></div>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Introduction</h2>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Shardtown propose deux bots Discord complémentaires : <strong class="text-white">ShardGuard</strong> pour la sécurité et la modération, et <strong class="text-white">Shard</strong> pour la gestion et l'animation de votre communauté. Les deux bots se configurent entièrement depuis le <strong class="text-white">dashboard web</strong>, sans commande complexe.
                        </p>
                        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                            <div class="p-4 bg-white/3 rounded-2xl border border-white/5">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                    <img src="/image/shardguard.png" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-xl" alt="">
                                    <span class="font-bold">ShardGuard</span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Sécurisation, vérification, modération automatique et gestion des accès.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="p-4 bg-white/3 rounded-2xl border border-white/5">
                                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
                                    <img src="/image/shard.png" class="w-8 h-8 rounded-xl" alt="">
                                    <span class="font-bold">Shard</span>
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Bienvenue, niveaux XP, salons vocaux temporaires et personnalisation du serveur.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- DASHBOARD -->
                    <div id="dashboard" class="wiki-card">
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                            <div class="step-badge"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8M12 17v4"/></svg></div>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">Dashboard Web</h2>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Le dashboard est l'interface principale pour configurer vos bots. Connectez-vous avec Discord, choisissez un serveur et modifiez les paramètres en temps réel.
                        </p>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="step-badge mt-0.5">1</div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Connexion Discord</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Cliquez sur <strong class="text-white">Dashboard</strong> depuis la page d'accueil et autorisez Shardtown à accéder à votre compte Discord.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="step-badge mt-0.5">2</div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Sélection du serveur</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Seuls les serveurs où vous avez la permission <strong class="text-white">Administrateur</strong> sont affichés. Choisissez le serveur à configurer.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="step-badge mt-0.5">3</div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Configuration en direct</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Toutes les modifications sont appliquées instantanément. Aucun redémarrage du bot n'est nécessaire.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="section-divider"></div>

                    <!-- SHARDGUARD HEADER -->
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-6">
                        <img src="/image/shardguard.png" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl" alt="">
                        <div>
                            <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold">ShardGuard</h2>
                            <p class="text-white/30 text-sm">Protection, modération et contrôle d'accès</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- SG - VERIFICATION -->
                    <div id="sg-verification" class="wiki-card">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="step-badge"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></div>
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Vérification par Captcha</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="feature-chip chip-guard">ShardGuard</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            Le système de vérification empêche les bots et raids de rejoindre votre serveur. Les nouveaux membres doivent résoudre un captcha visuel avant d'obtenir l'accès.
                        </p>
                        <div class="space-y-3 mb-6">
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="step-badge mt-0.5">1</div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Setup</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Utilisez <span class="var-tag">/setup-verification</span> dans votre serveur. Le bot envoie l'embed de vérification dans le salon actuel.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="step-badge mt-0.5">2</div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Rôle vérifié</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Configurez dans le dashboard le rôle à attribuer une fois le captcha réussi. Ce rôle donne accès aux salons du serveur.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="step-badge mt-0.5">3</div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Résolution du captcha</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Le membre clique sur le bouton, reçoit un captcha par MP et saisit le code via les boutons ou un formulaire. Le bot lui attribue le rôle en cas de succès.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-white/3 rounded-2xl border border-white/5 p-5">
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Options configurables</p>
                            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm">
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <span class="text-white/40">Nombre de chiffres</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white/70">4 – 8</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <span class="text-white/40">Niveau de bruit</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white/70">Faible / Moyen / Élevé</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <span class="text-white/40">Tentatives max</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white/70">1 – 10</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <span class="text-white/40">Délai avant kick</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white/70">1 – 60 min</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <span class="text-white/40">Code d'accès</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white/70">Optionnel</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                                    <span class="text-white/40">Kick automatique</span>
                                    <span class="font-bold text-white/70">Activable</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-4 p-4 bg-blue-500/5 border border-blue-500/10 rounded-xl">
                            <p class="text-xs text-blue-400/70 leading-relaxed"><strong class="text-blue-400">Code d'accès :</strong> Si activé, le membre doit d'abord entrer un mot de passe secret avant d'accéder au captcha. Utile pour les serveurs privés ou sur invitation uniquement.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- SG - AUTOMOD -->
                    <div id="sg-automod" class="wiki-card">
                        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-5">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                                <div class="step-badge"><svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
                                <h3 class="text-xl font-extrabold">Auto-Modération</h3>
                            </div>
                            <span class="feature-chip chip-guard">ShardGuard</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-white/50 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                            ShardGuard surveille les messages en temps réel et agit automatiquement selon vos règles. Chaque filtre est indépendant et configurable depuis le dashboard.
                        </p>
                        <div class="space-y-3">
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="4.93" y1="4.93" x2="19.07" y2="19.07"/></svg></div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Anti-Spam</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Détecte les envois de messages répétés en rafale. Action configurable : supprimer, avertir, mute ou kick.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-orange-500/10 border border-orange-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#fb923c" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71"/><path d="M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71"/></svg></div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Anti-Liens</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Bloque automatiquement les messages contenant des URLs. Idéal pour éviter la pub non souhaitée.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#facc15" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="4 7 4 4 20 4 20 7"/><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="15" y2="20"/><line x1="12" y1="4" x2="12" y2="20"/></svg></div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Anti-Caps</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Supprime les messages dont un pourcentage trop élevé est en majuscules. Seuil configurable.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="info-row">
                                <div class="w-7 h-7 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/20 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f87171" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polygon points="7.86 2 16.14 2 22 7.86 22 16.14 16.14 22 7.86 22 2 16.14 2 7.86 7.86 2"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg></div>
                                <div>
                                    <p class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">Mots Interdits</p>
                                    <p class="text-white/40 text-sm">Liste noire de mots ou expressions à bloquer. Chaque occurrence déclenche l'action définie.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mt-5 p-4 bg-white/3 rounded-xl border border-white/5">
                            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-white/30 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Actions disponibles</p>
                            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white/50">Supprimer</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white/50">Avertir</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white/50">Mute temporaire</span>
                                <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-white/5 rounded-full text-xs font-bold text-white/50">Kick</span>
